    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/aadc17d289638da5b1cdf3a6968e07b9.poster.avif?t=1724377146\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/aadc17d289638da5b1cdf3a6968e07b9.webm?t=1724377146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/aadc17d289638da5b1cdf3a6968e07b9.mp4?t=1724377146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你能在一个似乎没人在的阴郁城市里发现敌人的狙击手吗？<br><br>狙击手路是一个简单的游戏，你只需要前进。<br><br>然而，敌人的狙击手躲在建筑物之间。<br>你应该杀死所有的隐藏的敌人狙击手,到达目的地。<br><br>敌方狙击手的射程为200米。<br>如果你在敌人狙击手的射程之内，你就会被打败。<br><br>你必须检测隐藏的敌人，调整零点和火。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/6ee02a70855ae7318633fbc1dcb96b41.poster.avif?t=1724377146\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/6ee02a70855ae7318633fbc1dcb96b41.webm?t=1724377146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/6ee02a70855ae7318633fbc1dcb96b41.mp4?t=1724377146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>检测<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/468afa11ef40f2e18a80d84b026a899c.poster.avif?t=1724377146\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/468afa11ef40f2e18a80d84b026a899c.webm?t=1724377146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/468afa11ef40f2e18a80d84b026a899c.mp4?t=1724377146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>零点调整 (W, S)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/04fb11403200df63b22720a0405d49a8.poster.avif?t=1724377146\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/04fb11403200df63b22720a0405d49a8.webm?t=1724377146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/04fb11403200df63b22720a0405d49a8.mp4?t=1724377146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>扣動<br><br>您可以自定义您的玩家角色、枪和十字线。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/2e8a82862aa52dc4cd975856d8b54139.poster.avif?t=1724377146\" width=616 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/2e8a82862aa52dc4cd975856d8b54139.webm?t=1724377146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/2e8a82862aa52dc4cd975856d8b54139.mp4?t=1724377146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>有4个难度级别。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/53ee7dac90a01038c3e76ab9a5fb3a25.avif?t=1724377146\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><strong>容易</strong><br>此难度建议首次开始游戏的玩家使用。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/b8f0214b48a448f05aaff71b49fea0cf.avif?t=1724377146\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><strong>正常</strong><br>距离指南中有一些错误。有几个伪装的狙击手。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/13395af6369d3d8b92745da841a9eb8a.avif?t=1724377146\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><strong>困难</strong><br>不显示距离指南。有几个透明的敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811120/extras/058f2025ad8b425018ccbfb7e3551020.avif?t=1724377146\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><strong>千里眼</strong><br>你可以通过完成困难的来完成。最难的难度。",
